sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_083_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Upgrade Charge Point Security Profile - Accepted
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: SP 1 and/or 3 supported, current SP is 1 or 2

    Note over CP,CS: Manual Action: Send ChangeConfiguration for SecurityProfile

    CS->>CP: 1. ChangeConfiguration.req
    Note right of CS: key = SecurityProfile<br/>value = <current SP + 1>

    CP-->>CS: 2. ChangeConfiguration.conf
    Note left of CP: status = Accepted

    Note over CP,CS: Manual Action: Send Reset of type Hard

    CS->>CP: 3. Reset.req
    Note right of CS: type = Hard

    CP-->>CS: 4. Reset.conf
    Note left of CP: status = Accepted

    CP->>CS: 5. Reconnect with securityProfile + 1
    CS-->>CP: 6. Accept connection attempt

    CP->>CS: 7. BootNotification.req
    CS-->>CP: 8. BootNotification.conf
    Note right of CS: status = Accepted

    CP->>CS: 9. StatusNotification.req (per connector, connectorId=0)
    Note left of CP: status = Available
    CS-->>CP: 10. StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP,CS: Verify old security profile is rejected

    CP->>CS: 11. Reconnect with original securityProfile
    CS--xCP: 12. Central System rejects connection attempt

    Note over CP,CS: Restore connection with upgraded profile

    CP->>CS: 13. Reconnect with securityProfile + 1
    CS-->>CP: 14. Central System accepts connection attempt
